{"type": "article", "id": 18117, "title": "觉得铅笔就这么回事？你看，学生们完成了 18 种另类设计", "description": "觉得人生无聊吗，哈，让这些神奇的铅笔来拯救你！", "date": "2015-11-27T09:52:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3281, "name": "铅笔"}, {"id": 143, "name": "设计"}, {"id": 2575, "name": "文具"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 216, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105312BuORFQkPXCUADdvN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t“铅笔是很具体、很经典的设计对象。它们又简洁又实用，还有着强烈的历史和文化色彩。”\r\n设计师 <a href=\"http://www.luka.co.il/\">Luka Or</a> 在<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/11/24/holon-institute-of-technology-students-alternative-pencil-designs-rethinking-luka-or-keren-tomer/\" target=\"_blank\">接受媒体采访时说</a>，“因此我总是启发学生们，请他们从材质、功能、形式等维度重新设计铅笔。” <span style=\"text-align:left;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.luka.co.il/\">Luka Or</a><span style=\"text-align:left;\"> 所提及的，是 Holon Institute of Technology 大学的一个设计项目。项目的参与者是该校</span>工业设计专业的学生们，在设计师 <a href=\"http://www.luka.co.il/\">Luka Or</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.kulladesign.com/\">Keren Tomer</a> 的指导下，学生们完成了 18 种铅笔设计，样样精彩，我们挑了几个给你看看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">管状颜料和铅笔都是涂写工具，但它们一软一硬，材质和功用各不相同。它们结合起来会是什么样子？学生 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">Yam Amir 做出了大胆的尝试</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">。在使用他设计的铅笔时，你得把一端的“颜料管”往下卷才行。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105308CJzi2GfcO3FYxAaD.jpg\" title=\"Tube Pencil by Yam Amir\" alt=\"Tube Pencil by Yam Amir\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tube Pencil by Yam Amir</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105309FpzvciCW8Q4gJqxY.jpg\" title=\"Tube Pencil by Yam Amir\" alt=\"Tube Pencil by Yam Amir\" data-ratio=\"1.82051282\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Tube Pencil by Yam Amir</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">铅笔非要是细圆柱形的吗？不一定。Ofra Oberman 就设计了四款刷子状的铅笔，能画出粗粗的线条。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105309wky09oS5bPzumBfN.jpg\" title=\"Brusketch by Ofra Oberman\" alt=\"Brusketch by Ofra Oberman\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Brusketch by Ofra Oberman</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105310ZKbJixcQRfuCSwo2.jpg\" title=\"Brusketch by Ofra Oberman\" alt=\"Brusketch by Ofra Oberman\" data-ratio=\"1.29700855\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Brusketch by Ofra Oberman</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\">Roller Pencil by Noy Meiri，</span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">Noy Meiri 设计的铅笔有齿轮状的圆头，供服装设计师和平面设计师们使用。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071053101FioYB48sfSdw5WK.jpg\" title=\"Roller Pencil by Noy Meiri\" alt=\"Roller Pencil by Noy Meiri\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\">Gavish by Evgeny Barkov，</span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">Evgeny Barkov 追溯了铅笔设计的历史，设计了一款双头的木质铅笔。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105310sMWiNxYhgkCXfA9I.jpg\" title=\"Gavish by Evgeny Barkov\" alt=\"Gavish by Evgeny Barkov\" data-ratio=\"0.71581197\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105311SbujLNXm5DTQfRMU.jpg\" title=\"Waxcil by Gal Yacobi\" alt=\"Waxcil by Gal Yacobi\" data-ratio=\"0.66025641\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>Waxcil by Gal Yacobi，Gal Yacobi 设计的铅笔也是双头嗒！一头儿用于书写，另一头儿则用于封蜡。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105311UD7E9MsRpnGyLIXB.jpg\" title=\"Waxcil by Gal Yacobi\" alt=\"Waxcil by Gal Yacobi\" data-ratio=\"0.67200855\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\">Fairy Pencil by Eitan Bercovich，</span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">这款萌萌的铅笔被设计成了嘴和牙齿的形状。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105312y9E4mPzasfr7UxlM.jpg\" title=\"Fairy Pencil by Eitan Bercovich\" alt=\"Fairy Pencil by Eitan Bercovich\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t大师喜欢设计的是椅子和灯，因为它们实用，而且经典。现在看来，这个名单还应加上铅笔。铅笔作为最廉价的书写工具之一，除了实用功能外，还有情感上的价值。谁会忘记刚学会写字、歪歪扭扭写下自己名字的童年时代呢？我们审视日常用品，稍加质疑和联想，说不定哪天也能拥有自己的设计作品呐。\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/11/24/holon-institute-of-technology-students-alternative-pencil-designs-rethinking-luka-or-keren-tomer/\" target=\"_blank\">dezeen</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}